<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3166466" xml-lang="en-US" level="2" l10n="U" oldref="6">Fit Text to Frame</paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3150538" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG" oldref="8"><ahelp hid=".uno:TextFitToSizeTool">Draws a text box where you click or drag in the current document. The text that you enter is automatically resized to fit the dimensions of the text box.</ahelp> Click anywhere in the document, and then type or paste your text.</paragraph>
